OL,6,FThe cost of living, young people
OL,7,Ffeeling ignored and sea water quality
OL,8,Fare some of the key issues facing
OL,9,Fvoters in the Vale of Glamorgan.
OL,11,FThe constituency to the west of
OL,12,FCardiff has seen relatively little
OL,13,Fchange in last year's constituency
OL,14,Freview. It's kept its name, but had
OL,15,Fits boundary slightly reduced, with
OL,16,Fits easternmost corner becoming part
OL,17,Fof Cardiff South.
