OL,6,FThe people of this coastal
OL,7,Fconstituency have seen their fair
OL,8,Fshare of change when it comes to who
OL,9,Frepresents them in Westminster. It's
OL,10,Fan area which tends to reflect the
OL,11,Fmood of the UK in every general
OL,12,Felection for the past four decades.
OL,14,FITV1's Sharp End met candidates and
OL,15,Fvoters, who will be voting for the
OL,16,Ffirst time within the new electoral
OL,17,Fboundaries.
