OL,6,FSo important is opinion in the Vale of
OL,7,FGlamorgan that Prime Minister Rishi
OL,8,FSunak visited Barry on Day one of the
OL,9,Felection campaign. And a week later,
OL,10,FLabour leader Keir Starmer followed
OL,11,Fsuit. But the votes of young people
OL,12,Fhere on Barry Island are not so easily
OL,13,Fwon.
OL,15,F"We don't really know who to vote
OL,16,Ffor," said one young voter. "There's
OL,17,Fnot really a party for us."
OL,19,FHer friend added: "I feel like young
OL,20,Fpeople are often pushed aside,
OL,21,Fespecially Welsh young people."
