OL,6,FAnother first-time voter said MPs need
OL,7,Fgreater awareness to help out younger
OL,8,Fpeople and make sure that communities
OL,9,F"can keep going".
OL,11,FUse of food banks has been rising in
OL,12,Fthe constituency, due to the cost of
OL,13,Fliving crisis. That's according to the
OL,14,FChairperson at Castleland Community
OL,15,FCentre, Neil Moore.
