OL,6,FA weekly Foodshare project is run out
OL,7,Fof the community centre, which is
OL,8,Fsituated in the heart of Barry. Users
OL,9,Fof the service arrive at the centre
OL,10,Fand wait in a ticketed system before
OL,11,Fchoosing items they'd like.
OL,13,F"We kind of run it like a shop," Mr
OL,14,FMoore said, "so people come in and
OL,15,Fthey pick the items off the shelves so
OL,16,Fthey're only taking what they actually
OL,17,Fare going to use."
OL,19,FHe added: "There obviously is a huge
OL,20,Fdemand because of our numbers.
