OL,6,F"They've been steadily getting higher.
OL,7,FThe number of users that we get every
OL,8,Fweek has increased, especially in the
OL,9,Flast couple of years."
OL,11,FOne service user said: "It's expensive
OL,12,Fto live at the moment. Gas and
OL,13,Felectric need to go back down and cost
OL,14,Fof living need to go back down."
OL,16,FHer message to politicians? "Think
OL,17,Fabout other people before themselves -
OL,18,Fbecause they couldn't live like we do."
