OL,6,FIn the opposite side of this
OL,7,Fconstituency is Ogmore-by-Sea, home to
OL,8,Fone of the most popular beaches in
OL,9,FSouth Wales. But in this election
OL,10,Flocals say that tourism and water
OL,11,Fpollution should be some of the main
OL,12,Fpriorities for the next MP.
OL,14,FAnthony Evans has been selling ice
OL,15,Fcream from his van for 13 years and
OL,16,Fsays business is dying off. "There's
OL,17,Fnot enough people coming down," he
OL,18,Fsaid, "mainly it's the water pollution
OL,19,Fputting people off."
