OL,6,FHe added: "Easter time I was down 86%.
OL,7,FI would like hospitality to improve,
OL,8,Fdrop some of the rates on things and
OL,9,Ffor (the next government) to try and
OL,10,Fget people back down to the beach."
OL,12,FBeach-goer Amanda Monington says
OL,13,Fthere's been a "lack of investment in
OL,14,Fhuman beings in all its form and
OL,15,Finfrastructure."
