OL,6,FThe market town of Cowbridge is
OL,7,Ftraditionally a Conservative
OL,8,Fstronghold and voters there say they
OL,9,Fwant an MP they can trust, though many
OL,10,Fare still undecided.
OL,12,FOne shopper said the Conservative
OL,13,Fbetting scandal "makes you think you
OL,14,Fcan't trust people in that party."
OL,16,F"But if Labour did something as stupid
OL,17,Fas well, then maybe that would turn it
OL,18,Fround the other way."
